simzombie.engine.utils
Class Icons

java.lang.Object
  simzombie.engine.utils.Icons

public class Icons
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class that stores the package location of all relevant icons Also provides a way to retrieve an icon from file, and caches icons to improve on time spent reading from the disk
